{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/cenoura/awesome-ads/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"3362b2e3-c3b7-5aa9-bc3f-220ce305f222","html":"<h1 id=\"awesome-advertising-awesome\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#awesome-advertising-awesome\" aria-label=\"awesome advertising awesome permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Awesome Advertising <a href=\"https://awesome.re\"><img src=\"https://awesome.re/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a></h1>\n<p><strong>A curated list of advertising and programmatic media content and resources.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> I know people really dislike and, sometimes, get angry about ads on sites and apps. As they are widely used by individuals and companies to monetize, the main goal of this list is to share knowledge about how to implement it correctly and in an optimized way.</p>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#acronyms-and-abbreviations\">Acronyms and Abbreviations</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#concepts-and-fundamentals\">Concepts and Fundamentals</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#best-practices\">Best Practices</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#ad-managers--ad-servers--platforms\">Ad Managers / Ad Servers / Platforms</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#google-ad-manager\">Google Ad Manager</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#gam-libraries--tools\">GAM Libraries / Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#facebook--instagram\">Facebook / Instagram</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#programmatic\">Programmatic</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#header-bidding-hb\">Header Bidding (HB)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#prebid\">Prebid</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#prebid-libraries--tools\">Prebid Libraries / Tools</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#newsletters\">Newsletters</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"acronyms-and-abbreviations\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#acronyms-and-abbreviations\" aria-label=\"acronyms and abbreviations permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Acronyms and Abbreviations</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>AdOps: Advertising Operations</li>\n<li>AdX: Ad Exchange</li>\n<li>CPC: Cost Per Click</li>\n<li>CPM: Cost Per Mille</li>\n<li>CR: Conversion Rate</li>\n<li>CTR: Click Through Rate</li>\n<li>DFP: DoubleClick for Publishers</li>\n<li>DMP: Data Management Platform</li>\n<li>DSP: Demand Side Platform</li>\n<li>eCPM: Effective Cost Per Mille</li>\n<li>HB: Header Bidding</li>\n<li>RTB: Real Time Bidding</li>\n<li>SSP: Supply Side Platforms</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"concepts-and-fundamentals\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#concepts-and-fundamentals\" aria-label=\"concepts and fundamentals permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Concepts and Fundamentals</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.thinkwithgoogle.com/intl/en-145/perspectives/local-articles/what-does-ad-server-do-and-how-can-you-benefit-it/\">What does an Ad Server does and how can you benefit from it?</a> - Explain what an Ad Server do and how it can benefit your business.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://adzerk.com/blog/what-is-an-ad-server/\">What is an Ad Server</a> - Explain what an Ad Server is, Publisher vs Advertiser, why have one ad server.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"best-practices\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#best-practices\" aria-label=\"best practices permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Best Practices</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.betterads.org/\">Coalition for Better Ads</a> - A group of companies (Google, Facebook, etc) that publish research about how to improve the online consumer ad experience and defined some standards.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"ad-managers--ad-servers--platforms\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ad-managers--ad-servers--platforms\" aria-label=\"ad managers  ad servers  platforms permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Ad Managers / Ad Servers / Platforms</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://site.adform.com/\">Adform</a> - Advertising platform.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://adzerk.com/\">Adzerk</a> - Ad serving APIs to build and scale server-side ad platforms.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://admanager.google.com/\">Google Ad Manager (formerly DFP: DoubleClick for Publishers)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://displayvideo.google.com/\">Google Display &#x26; Video 360 (a.k.a DV360 / formerly DoubleClick Bid Manager)</a> - Integrated tool that helps creative, data, and media teams work together to execute end-to-end campaigns.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://smartadserver.com/\">Smart AdServer</a> - Ad Server.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"google-ad-manager\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#google-ad-manager\" aria-label=\"google ad manager permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Google Ad Manager</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://support.google.com/admanager/topic/7505788\">About Ad Manager and Ad Exchange</a> - Info about Google Ad Manager and Ad Exchange.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://support.google.com/admanager/topic/6048322\">Common problems / Troubleshooting</a> - How to solve common problems / issues with Google Ad Manager.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://skillshop.exceedlms.com/student/path/17117-drive-advertising-revenue-with-google-ad-manager\">Google Ad Manager Fundamentals</a> - Google Academy videos about Ad Manager (you should login to see the videos).</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://support.google.com/admanager/\">Help center</a> - Google Ad Manager Help Center.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://support.google.com/admanager/answer/9197913\">Release notes (2019)</a> - 2019 Google Ad Manager releases archive.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://support.google.com/admanager/topic/7505789\">Setup guide</a> - Guide to set up Google Ad Manager.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"gam-libraries--tools\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gam-libraries--tools\" aria-label=\"gam libraries  tools permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>GAM Libraries / Tools</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>React DFP - <a href=\"https://github.com/jaanauati/react-dfp\">GitHub</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/jaanauati/react-dfp\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">108</span></span></a> | <a href=\"http://react-dfp.ml/\">Docs</a> - React library to implement Google Ad Manager on your website.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"facebook--instagram\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#facebook--instagram\" aria-label=\"facebook  instagram permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Facebook / Instagram</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/business/learn\">Facebook Blueprint</a> - Online training for Advertising on Facebook and Instagram.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"programmatic\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#programmatic\" aria-label=\"programmatic permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h