-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">103</span></span></a> - An automated line item generator for Prebid.js and Google Ad Manager.</li>\n<li>React Prebid - <a href=\"https://github.com/technology-ebay-de/react-prebid\">GitHub</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/technology-ebay-de/react-prebid\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">29</span></span></a> | <a href=\"https://github.com/technology-ebay-de/react-prebid/wiki\">Docs</a> - React library to implement Google Ad Manager on your website.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"newsletters\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#newsletters\" aria-label=\"newsletters permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Newsletters</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://adprofs.co/this-week-in-ad-tech/\">AdProfs</a> - This week in ad tech - one email per week, 5 min read.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/business/m/updates-signup\">Business News from Facebook</a> - Latest updates, marketing trends and advertising tips from Facebook.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://simonjharris.substack.com\">Happy Friday by Simon J. Harris</a> - Ad tech info curated by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/SimonJHarris\">@SimonJHarris</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"contributing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contributing\" aria-label=\"contributing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contributing</h2>\n<p>Contributions to this list are always welcome! Take a look at <a href=\"https://github.com/cenoura/awesome-ads/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md\">contribution guidelines</a> and feel free to open a PR adding/updating items.</p>\n<h2 id=\"contact\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contact\" aria-label=\"contact permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contact</h2>\n<p>If you have any questions or suggestions about this list, do not hesitate to contact me on Twitter <a href=\"https://twitter.com/_seunoura\">@_seunoura</a> or <a href=\"https://github.com/cenoura/awesome-ads/issues/new\">open an issue</a>.</p>